The following hadiths also commands maintaining basic privacy in societal gathering: 
{{quotation|Narrated by Abu Said Khudri: The prophet said, "A man should not look at the private part of another man, and a woman should not look at the private parts of another woman. A man should not lie with another man without wearing lower garment under one cover; and a woman should not lie with another woman without wearing lower garment under one cover."|{{Hadith-usc|usc=yes|abudawud|31|4007}}}}

In another [[hadith]] it has been mentioned,
