*2004 ''[[The Road to Kandahar: On the Trail of bin Laden and Zawaheri]]''
*2007 ''[[(Un)Civil War of Words: Media and Politics in the Arab World]]'' ({{ISBN|0275993930}})
*2009 ''[[Kuwait and a New Concept of International Politics]]''

